## Limitations

The findings are based on secondary sources and may not capture the full complexity of the immigrant experience during the Market Revolution. Additionally, the role of immigrants varied significantly depending on their country of origin, which may not be fully represented in the available data. Further research using primary sources and more detailed demographic studies would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the immigrants' impact on the new market society.